## Worker API

### `POST /submit`

- Inputs
  - `"id"`: string, unique ID for job
  - `"url"`: string, URL to scribe
- Returns
  - `"status"`: `"pending"`
  - `"job_id"`: job ID

### `GET /status/<job_id>`

- Returns
  - `"completed"`: boolean
  - `"error"`: boolean
  - `"message"`: optional string, only when error == true
  - `"transcript"`: optional JSON, only when `completed == true`
  - `"stage"`: optional string, only when `!completed && !error`
